---
title: Easy Pork & Carrot Linguine with Parmesan Cheese & Balsamic-Apple Salad
description: You can add just about anything to a pasta, but sometimes simple and tasty is the way to go. We recommend cooking up a homey
combination of pork cooked in a creamy sauce with hints of earthen flavours from the carrot. Sprinkle some Parmesan cheese
and there you have it, a pasta that’s so simple you can cook it whenever you want!

